history.content:
It depends on 

1) where you are on section waitlists and 

2) how many people drop. 


There are no seat reserved for other students so no space if going to magically open up without folks dropping. 

(It is also possible that we would be able to add one more discussion section for CS70 in which case we will email the full waitlist to let you know how to maximize your chances for getting one of those spots. We won't know if that will happen until hours before it does so unfortunately I can't give you a good guess right now but pay attention to your email).
